Planets3D is a 3D gravitational simulator inspired by Planets (planets.homedns.org)
demo video: http://youtu.be/4ihB0k1ME10

Binary releases: http://sourceforge.net/projects/planets-3d/files/
Build using CMake (http://www.cmake.org)

Dependancies:
Qt 5 (http://qt-project.org) NOTE: at the moment the pre-built libraries on windows are built against OpenGL ES 2.0 which is NOT compatible. you must either build Qt yourself or find one built with desktop OpenGL.
GLM: (glm.g-truc.net)
